#: ../console-setup.templates:6001
msgid ""
"\"VGA\" has a traditional appearance and has medium coverage of "
"international scripts. \"Fixed\" has a simplistic appearance and has better "
"coverage of international scripts. \"Terminus\" may help to reduce eye "
"fatigue, though some symbols have a similar aspect which may be a problem "
"for programmers."
msgstr ""
"Mae gan \"VGA\" olwg traddodiadol ac yn cefnogi nifer cymhedrol o sgriptiau "
"rhyngwladol. Mae gan \"Fixed\" olwg syml a gwell cefnogaeth i sgriptiau "
"rhyngwladol. Fe all \"Terminus\" helpu leddfu blinder llygaid, ond mi fydd "
"rhai symbolau yn debyg a all fod yn broblem i raglennwyr."

